metadata.name: Loneliness
metadata.description:
Loneliness... A cup of coffee and a little furry friend at your feet. You sit down in a chair and immerse yourself in thoughts. You remember old friends and noisy parties. It's been a long time... You're not the same anymore. Time slows down, but it doesn't go backwards. 
____
The art was created using AI with subsequent digital processing.
Size: 11870 x 11870 px
